49:04.600 --> 49:06.670
♪ That I would treasure ♪

49:07.880 --> 49:10.997
♪ He said the rules don't apply ♪

49:11.080 --> 49:12.399
♪ To you ♪

49:15.240 --> 49:16.673
♪ In the movies we see ♪

49:16.760 --> 49:19.115
♪ In the shows on TV ♪

49:19.200 --> 49:22.237
♪ And in anthems passionately sung ♪

49:23.120 --> 49:24.633
♪ There's a message that you've got ♪

49:24.720 --> 49:26.870
♪ To keep believing in yourself ♪

49:27.920 --> 49:31.196
♪ But they generally mean
if you're young ♪

49:32.560 --> 49:36.917
♪ Is it written in the air
As it seems to be ♪

49:38.200 --> 49:42.796
♪ That we haven't long at all
