51:04.720 --> 51:05.856
This is all my fault.
This is my fault.

51:05.880 --> 51:06.976
No, no.
This is not your fault.

51:07.000 --> 51:08.831
This is all my fault.
This is my fault.

51:08.960 --> 51:10.791
And it's fine.
Let's face it, it's fine.

51:10.920 --> 51:11.920
I sang you the song.

51:12.000 --> 51:13.096
This is my fault.

