52:40.520 --> 52:41.555
Need help?

52:41.640 --> 52:44.359
No, thanks, Levar. I'm just gonna
change my clothes. Thanks, Frank.

52:47.440 --> 52:48.634
See you later.

52:50.800 --> 52:53.268
I hired you as my double
because you look exactly like me.

52:53.360 --> 52:55.191
The shoes are all wrong.
